<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,767,927]" pageId="0" pageNumber="630">• Mediumto large-sized marsupials; long, strong tails and highly developed hindlimbs and hindfeet; pelage mostly gray to brown with lighter underfur.</paragraph>
