<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,1129,1414]" pageId="0" pageNumber="630">• Diverse habitats from subalpine grasslands to tropical rainforests, dry woodlands, and sandy-stony deserts.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,1129,1414]" box="[1241,1954,1260,1289]" pageId="0" pageNumber="630">• 13 genera, 59 species,at least 88 extant taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,1129,1414]" pageId="0" pageNumber="630">• 2 species Critically Endangered, 8 species Endangered, 8 species Vulnerable; 1 subspecies Extinct in the Wild; 1 subspecies and 4 species Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
